-----------------------------
div background blur
.box{
    width: 50%;
    height: 50%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    position: absolute;
    background-color: white;
    left: 50%;
    top:50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    filter: grayscale(0.5) opacity(0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
}
------------------------------------------------------
remove filter from inner div
 filter: invert(100%);
